	<text>
		<body>
			<pb n="1R"/>
				<p rend="align(right)"><placeName>Savannah Ga</placeName></p>
				<p rend="align(right)"><date>19 Novr 1859</date></p>
				<p>Dear Sir&#44;</p>
			<p rend="indent(1)">I enclose you a chk&#58; for Twelve<lb/> dolls. in full for subscription to the<lb/> Occident to <date>March</date> next.  I request you<lb/> to sign &#38; return the above receipt.<lb/>  I think you <hi rend="underline">ought</hi> to collect your<lb/> subscriptions annually&#44; which you<lb/> might easily do through &#39;Adams&#39; Ex&#61;<lb/>&#61;press.  It is due to yourself &#38; to your<lb/> subscribers.  Many men can afford<lb/> to pay three dolls&#58; who can not<lb/> pay when years have accumulated<lb/> the sum to five or &#36;4 times that<lb/> amount.  You complain of the</p>
			<pb n="1V"/>
				<p>falling off of the subscribers to your<lb/> periodical &#38; oh how fervently do I<lb/> pray that you could see the real<lb/> cause of the decay of religion&#44; and of<lb/> interest in Judaism in the <placeName>United<lb/> States</placeName>.  In this country&#8212;practical<lb/> and <hi rend="underline">thinking</hi> as it is&#44; the mind<lb/> must be convinced&#44; &#38; it <sic>wont</sic> do<lb/> to tell men&#44; you must do thus&#44;<lb/> because your fathers did so&#44; for<lb/> this puts a stop to all progress &#38;<lb/> that is against the spirit of the<lb/> age&#8212;of every ten Americans&#44; who<lb/> are educated&#44; known to me&#44; mine<lb/> are in favor of a thorough change<lb/> of Synagogue worship&#8212;or service&#8212;<lb/> and yet I do not know one who</p>
			<pb n="2R"/>
				<p>would abrogate one particle of real<lb/> Judaism&#8212;they can not be made<lb/> to believe that the Religion which<lb/> God gave to his chosen people con&#61;<lb/>&#61;sists of my zitzith&#44; Lulab&#44; &#38; shophar&#8221;&#8212;<lb/> Forms &#38; ceremonies are necessary<lb/> &#38; proper&#44; but they are mere<lb/> out works to protect the inner<lb/> jewel&#44; &#38; must conform to the<lb/> tables of each succeeding age.<lb/>  And what is the result&#8212;educated<lb/> Jews become disgusted with the<lb/> antiquated forms&#44; &#38; keep away<lb/> from Synagogue.  But I have<lb/> said more than I intended&#44; &#38; only<lb/> in reply to your complaint.<lb/>  I love my <hi rend="underline">Religion</hi>&#44; &#38; I mourn<lb/> over its decay.</p>
			<p rend="indent(8)">Yr. Friend &#38; well wisher</p>
			<p rend="indent(9)"><persName role="author">Solomon Cohen</persName></p>
				<p>P.S. Now that I know how my a&#47;c<lb/> stands I will remit annually<lb/> <persName role="author">C</persName></p>
		</body>
